<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Set New Password</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="/js/validatePass.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <button class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 19.5L8.25 12l7.5-7.5" />
                </svg>
            </button>
            <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Thiết Lập Mật Khẩu</h1>
            <span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700">Tạo mật khẩu mới cho</p>
            <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold"><%=email%></p>
        </div>
        <form action="/resetPass/forgotPassPage" method="POST">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <div class="relative mt-1">
                    <label for="password" class="block text-gray-700">Mật khẩu</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password"
                        class="w-full px-4 py-2 mt-1 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500"
                        required oninput="validatePassword()" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="message" class="alert alert-danger text-center text-red-500">
                <%= message%>
            </div>
         
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                <span id="condition-lowercase">• Ít nhất một ký tự viết thường.</span><br>
                <span id="condition-uppercase">• Ít nhất một ký tự viết hoa.</span><br>
                <span id="condition-length">• 8-16 ký tự.</span><br>
                <span id="condition-valid-chars">• Chỉ các chữ cái, số và ký tự phổ biến mới có thể được sử dụng.</span>
            </p>
            <input type="hidden" id="email" name="email" value="<%= email %>">
            <input type="hidden" id="uniqueString" name="uniqueString" value="<%= uniqueString %>">
            <button type="submit" class="w-full py-2 px-4  bg-indigo-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-orange-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:ring-offset-2" disabled>TIẾP TỤC</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
